OpenFPC Project.

Still under dev, not ready for usage yet. 

Notes on actions that can be sent by client to proxy or slave devices.

fetch         Fetch pcap and return to client/server
store         Request data for extraction, and disconnect.
status        Provide status of an OpenFPC Node
ctxupdate     Force a connection summary updae 
summary	      Fetch a connection summery 
ctxclean      Clean out stale connections (older than we have a pcap for)
ctxsearch     Get traffic/connection tables between starttime/endtime	FUTURE
replay        Replay traffic (FUTURE)

